org.richfaces.resource.mapping

Interface ResourceMapper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertiesResourceMapper

    public interface ResourceMapper
    Allows to programatically configure Resource Mapping, it means for resource key it can decide that the resource is re-mapped to another resource. All the ResourceMappers will be checked to determine mapping - first resource mapper which comes will be used.
    Author:
    Lukas Fryc

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ResourceMapping mapResource(ResourceKey resourceKey)
      Determines whether resource identified by given key is mapped to another resource.

    • Method Detail

      • mapResource

        ResourceMapping mapResource(ResourceKey resourceKey)
        Determines whether resource identified by given key is mapped to another resource.
        Parameters:
        resourceKey - the key of the resource to be checked for existence of its mapping
        Returns:
        the mapping for a resource given by a key; or null if no mapping is specified by this
